				<wikidot:authorName>shortskirts</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2525069</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't identify any of the &quot;easter eggs,&quot; but that doesn't matter much. This skip stands well on its own. The sheer contrast between the two reincarnated souls allows for delightful absurdity while painting a broad picture of what's transpired to bring these two entities to this situation. I'm delighted to see that there's an abundance of SCPs with acceptable levels of silliness in their ultimate delivery.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
