					<![CDATA[
						 <p>These two trees are probably some of my favorite characters on the site just due to how they're written and juxtaposed between each other. I'm in love with this skip. This is absolutely ripe for writing material too, from exploring the two trees and their time together, to the Knife God, to Saturn Deer, to <em>Horror at the Honey Glazed Abyss</em>, to Skybound Antelope Reincarnation Services, to&#8230;</p> <p>So much well-written stuff in here. +1 all the way.</p> 
				 	]]>
