					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-659029#post-2064695</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-659029/scp-1710#post-2064695</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 06 Jul 2014 15:36:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Voct</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>392303</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>You've got things blurred. Sharpy was chasing 682 when it came to Earth, that's obvious, but it was incidental. &quot;It tricked me into coming here&quot; is just Sharpy's self-justifying &quot;it was someone else's fault&quot; excuse. &quot;I didn't make a bad decision in coming to this world of crude physicality, I was lied to! I was deceived!&quot;</p> <p>682 had nothing to do with reincarnating Sharpy as a tree; that was Saturn Deer, and that <em>was</em> lies and deceit.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
