					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm a bit late to this party, but am I the only one who thinks that the creature that tricked Sharpy (1710-1) is SCP-682? Something that could be ripped, dissected and overwhelmed utterly, but won't die? Something &quot;cunning, fast and <strong>adaptive</strong>&quot;? Particularly the line &quot;hid in its own torment&quot;, seems to indicate 682. It always seemed rather tormented by our reality (at least from its perspective). But maybe it's just me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
